FBIS3-26638 "drchi028_k_94011" FBIS-CHI-94-028 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Feb 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Li Peng Signs Religious Places Activities Rules OW0902050594 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0910 GMT 5 Feb 94 OW0902050594 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service Language: Chinese Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, 5 Feb (XINHUA) -- Decree No. 145 of the State Council of the People's Republic of China: The "Regulations on the Management of the Places of Religious Activities" are hereby promulgated for implementation effective on the day of promulgation. [Signed] Premier Li Peng [Dated] 31 January 1994
